ns":[{"id":"f29fac32-95d5-4bea-8d81-79f201902b61","label":"Corruption Track","blocks":[{"id":"18b8dcd1-43a5-456b-a4a6-a9d8a23db874","label":"Corruption ","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false},{"label":"","checked":false},{"label":"","checked":false},{"label":"","checked":false},{"label":"","checked":false}]}]},{"id":"5b84a7b9-a2a5-444e-8efa-6ffc6f5eadd8","label":"Corruption Advances","blocks":[{"id":"24960178-6807-4605-b525-a4aeba10ff1e","label":"Take a corruption move","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"68d004f4-05ae-4ed8-9083-22399d8e09c8","label":"Take a corruption move","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"c6b809e1-1799-4a7c-8ad5-f52e0ea99195","label":"Take a corruption move","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"863365b2-d76d-475f-ab38-95a5638398b2","label":"Take a corruption move from another Archetype","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"97227ddd-d500-4ef2-a058-24b5a86121c3","label":"Retire your character. They may return as a Threat.","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]}]}]},{"sections":[{"id":"fc85764c-0371-442d-9e10-3e7c3438d39c","label":"Corruption Moves","blocks":[{"id":"719656b6-644c-4ca3-957e-46448807b010","label":"True Hunter","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":[],"helperText":"&nbsp;Mark corruption when pursuing a human NPC at night. Your<br>prey cannot escape you, no matter where they attempt to flee, and you<br>can prey on them or kill them at will.&nbsp;"}},{"id":"dd18c58b-2f00-4d04-85be-3e461aa94783","label":"Adaptable Palate","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":[],"helperText":"You can feed on any creature, not just humans. Feeding on something wildly different than a human will have unexpected side<br>effects."}},{"id":"f05e8976-b429-4995-997c-51154daec8be","label":"Pull Them Back In","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":[],"helperText":": When you *cash in your last Debt* on someone in<br>your web, mark corruption to keep the Debt and keep them in your web"}},{"id":"e1c6882f-baf8-4714-be0a-ad1dd5a700f6","label":"Blood Magic","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":[],"helperText":"Choose 2 faerie powers. Mark corruption to use one of<br>these powers"}}]}]}]}],"label":"Corruption"},{"id":"3d21b55e-1c47-4727-825f-04fd4065b405","rows":[{"columns":[{"sections":[{"id":"bd29c2ea-2621-41e4-8c15-2cff9a6f5cef","label":"The Vampire's Web","blocks":[{"id":"ed9f83c9-3787-42ef-8019-c8ed14de045f","label":"When someone comes to you to ask for a favor, look for advice/info, or<br>threaten your interests, they enter your *web* and owe you a Debt. When<br>someone is in your web, you gain the following when dealing with them:<br>     • Get +1 ongoing to *lend* a hand or *get* in the way of their efforts<br>     • Add this question to *figure someone out*: “What is your character’s true hunger?”<br>At the start of a session, choose someone in your web and learn a secret<br>about them that they’d rather keep buried.\n<br>They leave your web only when they no longer owe you a Debt.","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{}}]}]}]},{"columns":[{"sections":[{"id":"ba161b78-0548-43d9-9ad1-b6c7823147b3","label":"Debts","blocks":[{"id":"a9ba8277-b8a5-42a2-bd99-60d7ed4ff24e","label":"• Someone makes sure you get fed regularly. You owe them<br>2 Debts","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{}},{"id":"4f588561-91a0-4a71-8e02-a1df7945bc27","label":"• Someone relies on you for their fix. They owe you a Debt","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{}},{"id":"71a63e9d-2704-4eb5-af97-4b44d824c4d9","label":"• Someone bears responsibility for you becoming a vampire. They<br>owe you a Debt","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{}}]}]}]},{"columns":[{"sections":[{"id":"ff61a6f3-1fef-4f46-b399-1ff252ce0f12","label":"Vamp Moves","blocks":[{"id":"2ed215eb-4163-441c-962e-d4d3e19c1a87","label":"Eternal Hunger","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":["2d6"],"helperText":"&nbsp;You hunger for human blood, flesh, or emotions, pick<br>one. When you feed, roll with Blood. On a 10+, choose 3. On a 7-9,<br>choose 2:<br>• You heal 1-harm<br>• You learn a secret about them<br>• You take +1 forward<br>• They don’t die<br>On a miss, something goes terribly wrong","hideModifier":false}},{"id":"d5554a45-27e4-428a-93bc-e262dbdf4e50","label":"Info Text","type":"InfoText","value":"And choose two more:","meta":{}},{"id":"59480eda-7c72-4ad7-95f1-69531f967b33","label":"Irresistible","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":["2d6"],"helperText":"When you *persuade an NPC* using promises or seduction,<br>treat a 7-9 as a 10+ result. On a miss, your machinations succeed as<br>though you rolled a 7-9, but attract the attention of a rival or enemy."}},{"id":"4357597f-a9a8-4522-9892-d1cbb909abe7","label":"Haven","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":["2d6"],"helperText":"&nbsp;You have a safe place, secure from outside dangers. It has<br>emergency rations, a few ghouls, and an escape vector. When someone<br>willingly comes to your haven, they enter your web."}},{"id":"b771e011-65ed-4b5e-81a0-e4f43ecab155","label":"Cold-Blooded","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":["2d6"],"helperText":"When you *keep your cool* under emotional duress, roll<br>with Blood instead of Spirit"}},{"id":"b891930a-656e-4569-abe8-06c35bc153eb","label":"Keep Your Friends Close","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":["2d6"],"helperText":"When you *figure someone out* by indulging<br>their vices, roll with Blood instead of Mind."}},{"id":"81b805d1-da2a-43b6-b28f-6c45a6dd19e4","label":"Put Out the Word","type":"Skill","value":"0","meta":{"checked":false,"commands":["2d6"],"helperText":"When you *cash in a Debt* with someone in your web,<br>add this option to the list:<br>• Put out the word with their Faction that you want something. You<br>get +3 forward to *hit the streets* with that Faction"}}]}]},{"sections":[{"id":"cbb3aa01-78d8-4fec-acd2-3d9885da4e18","label":"Drama Moves","blocks":[{"id":"eb46b2d1-b14f-4866-a1a2-d15e1f88c881","label":"Vamp Corruption Move<br>","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{"helperText":"When you feed on an unwilling victim, mark corruption.&nbsp;"}},{"id":"acfae585-684d-41f1-ae3b-8b835a1377a1","label":"Vamp Intimacy Move<br>","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{"helperText":"When you share a moment of intimacy—physical or emotional—with another<br>person, tell them a secret about yourself or owe them a Debt. Either way,<br>they enter your web and owe you a Debt"}},{"id":"aca6e0a6-2815-47ce-b926-12f7321d7a3f","label":"Vamp End Move<br>","type":"Text","value":"","meta":{"helperText":"When you die or retire your character, name someone in the scene you want<br>dead; your agents and allies relentlessly pursue them.&nbsp;"}}]}]}]}],"label":"Moves"},{"id":"786a4f00-b826-459d-b6f6-2ce53cdd8f27","rows":[{"columns":[{"sections":[{"id":"7f17e525-db58-4ebe-a164-0fd616cc00eb","label":"Standard Avances","blocks":[{"id":"ff06049b-95d7-48d4-8c16-407ddf15bde7","label":"+1 Blood (max +3) ","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"2b9251b1-aa5a-49cd-b289-1d9f73b74864","label":"+1 Heart (max +3)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"f2ab1d2b-03e7-46a9-81b9-ddd86554de5f","label":"+1 Mind (max +3)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"88e2a673-f700-4bfd-871e-b2343f8e5296","label":"+1 Spirit (max +3)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"756a711d-5138-417b-9c88-d4cc8e913489","label":"A new Vamp Move","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"d31d7854-0752-45e0-84d0-99f9f1ca7b95","label":"A new Vamp Move","type":"Sl