:"Change to a new Archetype","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]}]}]}]}],"label":"Advances"},{"id":"b42738b6-75b3-4bda-9d45-0ad5af585409","rows":[{"columns":[{"sections":[{"id":"af57e7d3-6702-4961-82b4-6679356eae1f","label":"Harm","blocks":[{"id":"770ddc44-aecf-4fc1-bb51-6160d273faa3","label":"Faint","type":"Numeric","value":"1","meta":{"checked":false}},{"id":"3a74bbf8-2e2b-465e-a39d-394637e90602","label":"Faint","type":"Numeric","value":"1","meta":{"checked":false}},{"id":"b895719c-c15c-4232-a187-eae322de6bb5","label":"Grievous","type":"Numeric","value":"2","meta":{"checked":false}},{"id":"a1a8128a-a809-414e-8d45-57fe18c6201e","label":"Grievous","type":"Numeric","value":"2","meta":{"checked":false}},{"id":"d8ba8e95-44da-4949-b9f1-6f5a73458231","label":"Critical","type":"Numeric","value":"3","meta":{"checked":false}},{"id":"93ae2780-4133-4235-a4e9-5173af1adc11","label":"Critical","type":"Numeric","value":"3","meta":{"checked":false}}]},{"id":"b5d67c04-3794-450b-a820-c95c9d3c8513","label":"Armor","blocks":[{"id":"aa368156-327c-44d5-bf3e-8c23ec6d8dd8","label":"Current Armor Rating","type":"PointCounter","meta":{"isMainPointCounter":false},"value":"0"}]}]},{"sections":[{"id":"7a10365c-dd59-4f3c-833e-4f2429e3b1bc","label":"S-Harm","blocks":[{"id":"eca702fc-b0b2-4629-8fc0-d2515180d4dd","label":"Incapacitated","type":"Numeric","value":"1","meta":{"checked":false}}]},{"id":"da5c0a9e-c9e6-4cd5-86d8-a831eb7a1d42","label":"Scars","blocks":[{"id":"b2ff339d-5baa-481c-ac46-06f7822608c4","label":"Shattered (-1 Blood)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{"helperText":"Shattered means frightened, weakened, and overly cautious. Shattered characters hesitate when they should move, and their attempts to unleash an<br>attack on someone or escape a situation often come up short."},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"0f572c28-74ac-4761-acb0-8ab18859c693","label":"Crushed (-1 Heart)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{"helperText":"Crushed means traumatized, timid, and uncertain. Crushed characters bear<br>the full weight of the wounds they’ve suffered, and their attempts to persuade an NPC are inhibited by their reticent approach to conflict."},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"48b2e9b7-5bd1-44ed-b592-75c80c1355ea","label":"Fractured (-1 Mind)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{"helperText":"Fractured means confused, disoriented, and disjointed. Fractured characters<br>are unstable and unsure, and their attempts to figure someone out or mislead, distract, or trick others are unfocused and imprecise."},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]},{"id":"4dc26522-6cee-4d50-a3e5-5ca78a4d8256","label":"Broken (-1 Spirit)","type":"SlotTracker","meta":{"helperText":"Broken means hopeless, forlorn, and cowardly. Broken characters have lost<br>their will to fight, and their attempts to keep their cool or let it out are often<br>half-hearted and incomplete."},"value":[{"label":"","checked":false}]}]}]}]}],"label":"Harm"}],"template":"Blank","version":6,"wide":true,"group":"Urban Shadows Archetypes"}